snippet.textDisplay: One day in France, I was stuck in a traffic jam in my car, this song playing... I was looking at my mobile. A policeman knocked at my door window I jumped by surprise. I opened the glass and he told me it was forbidden to look at mobile while I was driving....and then the song went "Reedaha reedaha Kefima reedaha !" He listened to this and then told me "you can go" and didn't give any fine... Oufff... As he looked as if he was from Algerian or Moroccan family I don't know if he understood the words...but anyway it seemed to have an impact on him... :-D  thanks to this song !
